@DATABASE "E!-PAGER.Guide"
@NODE MAIN "E!-PAGER v1.20 Documentation - Contents"

      E!-PAGER v1.20 (C)1992-93 by Janne Siren, All Rights Reserved
      =============================================================

 Welcome to E!-PAGER v1.20, this is the third major release and contains
 several new features like the split screen chat. I have also fixed many
 bugs and replaced most routines with faster and smaller ones. There are
 no ASCII configuration files anymore and configuration utility has been
 rewritten and redesigned for maximum convenience. External programs are
 executed asynchronously so everything runs without delays and smoothly.

              @{"           Description and Updates           " link EG-0.0 }
